== StartUp-Manager ==

StartUp-Manager is obsolete, its development is stopped since <2011.
StartUp-Manager is incompatible with Ubuntu 11.10 and newer versions of Ubuntu.

You may want to use <nowiki>[[https://launchpad.net/grub-customizer|GRUB-Customizer]]</nowiki> instead.
